                              NSSDC User Survey
                     ___________________________________

   The National Space Science Data Center (NSSDC) at NASA/Goddard Space
   Flight Center (GSFC) offers a range of services to a diverse user
   community. This user survey is intended to identify areas in which
   NSSDC is being more or less effective in satisfying user needs. We
   solicit your comments on:
     * the relative priorities of our various services
     * the quality of our products and services
     * the effectiveness of the interfaces (human and electronic)
     * services not presently offered by NSSDC

   The survey is in parts. Feel free to address any or all parts. Part 1,
   below, is the most important.

   Part 2 addresses your computer environment and format preferences.

   Part 3 requests goodness scores for each of many services.

   Thanks very much for your feedback.

                        [ Part 1 | Part 2 | Part 3 ]

